```python

Class Square:

    Def __init__(self, size=0):

        If not isinstance(size, int):

            Raise TypeError(“size must be an integer”)

        Elif size < 0:

            Raise ValueError(“size must be ≥ 0”)

        Else:

            Self.__size = size



    Def area(self):

        Return self.__size ** 2



    @property

    Def size(self):

        Return self.__size



    @size.setter

    Def size(self, value):

        If not isinstance(value, int):

            Raise TypeError(“size must be an integer”)

        Elif value < 0:

            Raise ValueError(“size must be ≥ 0”)

        Else:

            Self.__size = value

```



